      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="Y48A33IL">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Y48A33IL-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y48A33IL-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y48A33IL-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">The following Lines are said to be written by Dr. S<hi rend="small-caps">WIFT</hi> to a Friend, who asked him which were his favourite Furniture.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Y48A33IL-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y48A33IL-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y48A33IL-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Y48A33IL-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y48A33IL-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y48A33IL-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HE Furniture that best doth please</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-2" n="2">St. <hi rend="italics">Patrick</hi>'s Dean, good Sir, are these;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-3" n="3">The <hi rend="italics">Knife</hi> and <hi rend="italics">Fork</hi>, with which I <hi rend="italics">eat</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-4" n="4">And next the <hi rend="italics">Pot</hi> that <hi rend="italics">boils</hi> the <hi rend="italics">Meat</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-5" n="5">The next to be preferr'd, I think,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-6" n="6">Is the <hi rend="italics">Glass</hi> in which I <hi rend="italics">drink</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-7" n="7">The Shelves on which my <hi rend="italics">Books</hi> I keep,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-8" n="8">And the <hi rend="italics">Bed</hi> in which I <hi rend="italics">sleep</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-9" n="9">An Antique <hi rend="italics">Elbow Chair</hi> between,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-10" n="10">Big enough to hold the Dean;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-11" n="11">And the <hi rend="italics">Stove</hi> that gives Delight,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-12" n="12">In the cold, bleak, wintry Night:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-13" n="13">To these we add a Thing <hi rend="italics">below</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-14" n="14">More for <hi rend="italics">Use</hi> reserv'd than <hi rend="italics">Shew</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-15" n="15">These are what the Dean do please;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A33IL-line-16" n="16">All <hi rend="italics">superfluous</hi> are but <hi rend="italics">these</hi>.
Y48A33IL   </l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
